room_title: Escape room "Narcos" by Panic Escape Room in Chicago
room_address: 1000 W Spring St South Elgin, IL 60177
room_description: Current Sinaloa cartel leader Ismael Zambada Garcia was captured fleeing Mexico, with a reduction in cartel members in us. Your team is up to the task of being the new recruits. Your task is to get into the drug warehouse collect the drugs and money, find a way to bust him out of his cell before he gets transported to a federal prison. Don’t make a scene and don’t get caught! If you succeed you are now part of the largest active cartels! If you fail you go down and do federal time!
